item.title: Talha Okur
item.description: Exprience Nokia I am working as an Applied R&D Engineer on Charging Systems at Nokia. March 2022 - Present Gazi University During my two years at Gazi University I was a Research and Teaching Assistant at Computer Engineering Department. I gain exprience on teaching while sharpening my skills on Programming, Data Science and Distributed Systems. I’d assisted given lectures: Database Management Systems Web Programming Object Oriented Programming Mobile Application Development on Android Application Development for IoT Devices March 2020 - February 2022
